about.summary: A programmatic interface to many species occurrence data sources, including Global Biodiversity Information Facility ('GBIF'), 'USGSs' Biodiversity Information Serving Our Nation ('BISON'), 'iNaturalist', Berkeley 'Ecoinformatics' Engine, 'eBird', Integrated Digitized 'Biocollections' ('iDigBio'), 'VertNet', Ocean 'Biogeographic' Information System ('OBIS'), and Atlas of Living Australia ('ALA'). Includes functionality for retrieving species occurrence data, and combining those data.

A programmatic interface to many species occurrence data sources, including Global Biodiversity Information Facility ('GBIF'), 'USGSs' Biodiversity Information Serving Our Nation ('BISON'), 'iNaturalist', Berkeley 'Ecoinformatics' Engine, 'eBird', Integrated Digitized 'Biocollections' ('iDigBio'), 'VertNet', Ocean 'Biogeographic' Information System ('OBIS'), and Atlas of Living Australia ('ALA'). name: r-spocc
raw_meta_yaml:
{% set version = "1.2.0" %}
{% set posix = 'm2-' if win else '' %}
{% set native = 'm2w64-' if win else '' %}

package:
  name: r-spocc
  version: {{ version|replace("-", "_") }}

source:
  url:
    - {{ cran_mirror }}/src/contrib/spocc_{{ version }}.tar.gz
    - {{ cran_mirror }}/src/contrib/Archive/spocc/spocc_{{ version }}.tar.gz
  sha256: 4bac45db5e69bfa3bf6cebd1b0c9241214c95561f275cee6d31e00911aa79d84

build:
  merge_build_host: true  # [win]
  number: 0
  noarch: generic
  rpaths:
    - lib/R/lib/
    - lib/

requirements:
  build:
    - {{ posix }}zip               # [win]
  host:
    - r-base
    - r-crul
    - r-data.table
    - r-jsonlite
    - r-lubridate
    - r-rbison
    - r-rebird
    - r-rgbif
    - r-ridigbio
    - r-rvertnet
    - r-tibble
    - r-wellknown
    - r-whisker
  run:
    - r-base
    - r-crul
    - r-data.table
    - r-jsonlite
    - r-lubridate
    - r-rbison
    - r-rebird
    - r-rgbif
    - r-ridigbio
    - r-rvertnet
    - r-tibble
    - r-wellknown
    - r-whisker

test:
  commands:
    - $R -e "library('spocc')"           # [not win]
    - "\"%R%\" -e \"library('spocc')\""  # [win]

about:
  home: https://github.com/ropensci/spocc (devel), https://ropensci.github.io/spocc/ (user manual)
  license: MIT
  summary: A programmatic interface to many species occurrence data sources, including Global Biodiversity Information Facility ('GBIF'), 'USGSs' Biodiversity Information Serving Our Nation ('BISON'), 'iNaturalist', Berkeley 'Ecoinformatics' Engine, 'eBird', Integrated Digitized 'Biocollections' ('iDigBio'), 'VertNet', Ocean
    'Biogeographic' Information System ('OBIS'), and Atlas of Living Australia ('ALA'). Includes functionality for retrieving species occurrence data, and combining those data.
  license_family: MIT
  license_file:
    - {{ environ["PREFIX"] }}/lib/R/share/licenses/MIT
    - LICENSE

extra:
  recipe-maintainers:
    - conda-forge/r
